item.title: Compile Error
item.dc:creator: @Slave_Scyth Slave Scyth
item.description:
@Slave_Scyth wrote:

[quote=“jc22493, post:8, topic:268998”]Your constructor names and class names must be identical, even case-wise.[/quote]^^ That.

To elaborate even more, though, go to the top of your Client.java.

Checked mine, and the Client class IS capitalized:

class Client extends Player implements Runnable {

Try changing “public client” to “public Client”.
